WEBVTT

01:44.120 --> 01:44.719
Run!

01:45.200 --> 01:46.280
Awesome!

01:46.400 --> 01:46.920
Great job!

01:46.920 --> 01:48.000
Sandy, you're amazing!

01:48.200 --> 01:49.239
Slacking off again.

01:49.640 --> 01:50.760
Give it to me!

01:51.239 --> 01:51.840
Fantastic!

01:51.840 --> 01:52.799
So impressive! Great job!

01:52.799 --> 01:53.640
Look how well they're playing.

01:53.959 --> 01:54.920
You're really smart.

01:55.400 --> 01:56.319
Do it again! One more time!

01:56.799 --> 01:57.840
Slacking off again, no eating.

01:57.920 --> 01:58.680
You can't eat this time.

01:58.799 --> 01:59.519
Auntie Yu.

01:59.519 --> 02:00.439
You're always slacking off.

02:01.079 --> 02:01.719
Come here.

02:01.879 --> 02:02.599
Auntie Yu.

02:03.040 --> 02:04.200
I bought you

02:04.640 --> 02:06.120
the latest style scarf.

02:06.239 --> 02:07.599
I don't know if you'll like it.

02:13.039 --> 02:13.439
Miss Xu.

02:13.439 --> 02:14.120
Next time, I can too.

02:15.599 --> 02:16.919
Miss Xu, what did you buy?

02:16.960 --> 02:17.520
Let me see.

02:19.240 --> 02:20.360
A cashmere scarf.

02:21.520 --> 02:22.319
Miss Xu.

02:23.199 --> 02:24.000
You got it wrong.

02:24.639 --> 02:26.599
Your future mother-in-law usually likes

02:26.919 --> 02:28.599
plain colors.

02:29.120 --> 02:30.759
She doesn't like patterns.

02:32.000 --> 02:33.199
Ms. Ma,

02:33.479 --> 02:35.680
if she hasn't paid attention before,

02:35.719 --> 02:37.199
how would she know?

02:37.759 --> 02:39.039
You need to pay attention.

02:39.199 --> 02:41.280
Otherwise, you'll embarrass yourself in the future.

02:41.479 --> 02:42.319
Miss Xu.

02:43.000 --> 02:44.240
Cashmere scarves

02:44.280 --> 02:46.080
have a lot of details to consider.

02:46.319 --> 02:49.120
The higher the yarn count, the softer it feels.

02:49.240 --> 02:50.879
The one you picked

02:51.280 --> 02:52.800
she definitely won't wear it.

02:53.039 --> 02:53.960
Xiaobu.

02:54.280 --> 02:54.960
Here.

02:55.319 --> 02:55.960
Baby.

02:56.479 --> 02:57.199
Xiaobu.

02:57.240 --> 02:57.800
Come.

02:58.520 --> 02:59.159
Thank you.

03:01.919 --> 03:02.879
Amy, come here.

03:14.479 --> 03:15.120
Little Xu.

03:16.960 --> 03:18.360
But since it's from Little Xu,

03:18.599 --> 03:19.400
it's also from Italy,

03:19.400 --> 03:20.759
a 100% cashmere scarf.

03:20.800 --> 03:21.759
It's a good item.

03:22.800 --> 03:23.520
Back then,

03:23.759 --> 03:24.800
when I was in school,

03:25.039 --> 03:25.919
I didn't study hard.

03:26.039 --> 03:27.319
I was always traveling.

03:27.439 --> 03:28.439
When I was short on money,

03:28.479 --> 03:29.479
I even used cashmere scarves

03:29.560 --> 03:30.439
to exchange for cash.

03:31.039 --> 03:32.360
That's why it's called cashmere.

03:34.280 --> 03:34.919
This color

03:34.919 --> 03:36.360
I already have too many of them.

03:36.680 --> 03:38.360
It suits your fair skin.

03:39.080 --> 03:40.120
Keep it for yourself.

03:44.080 --> 03:44.680
Little Xu, I'll be right back.

03:44.719 --> 03:45.560
Xiaobu, over here.

03:47.360 --> 03:48.240
Great job!

03:49.759 --> 03:50.360
Come here.

03:51.319 --> 03:51.919
Xiaobu.

03:52.759 --> 03:53.520
Xiaobu.

03:55.639 --> 03:56.240
Alan.

03:57.360 --> 03:58.840
I think this girl

03:59.120 --> 04:00.879
doesn't have good taste in any aspect.

04:01.719 --> 04:02.800
You should think it over.

04:03.400 --> 04:04.719
Don't rush to set the wedding date.

04:16.160 --> 04:16.800
Claire.

04:18.160 --> 04:18.600
Come.

04:34.199 --> 04:35.000
I've chosen.

04:36.680 --> 04:37.519
Miss Xu.

04:37.959 --> 04:39.199
You're really kind.

04:39.360 --> 04:40.560
You're not pretentious at all.

04:40.560 --> 04:42.000
You even came shopping with me.

04:42.800 --> 04:43.839
It's because Haochen and Haoming

04:43.879 --> 04:44.600
both love

04:44.600 --> 04:46.079
your cooking so much.

04:46.279 --> 04:47.199
You can cook Chinese food

04:47.439 --> 04:48.279
and Western food,

04:48.560 --> 04:49.759
everything.

04:50.519 --> 04:51.000
Sister Hui.

04:51.040 --> 04:52.519
You have to teach me when you have time.

04:53.319 --> 04:54.839
I've been cooking for a long time.

04:54.959 --> 04:56.279
So I have some experience.

04:57.000 --> 04:57.600
Miss Xu.

04:58.000 --> 04:59.079
Can you get me a box of lychees?

04:59.560 --> 05:00.040
Sure.

05:03.759 --> 05:04.439
Is that okay?

05:05.360 --> 05:06.040
Yes, of course.

05:06.040 --> 05:06.800
I'll put it down then.

05:06.959 --> 05:07.439
Thank you.

05:07.600 --> 05:08.079
No problem.

05:08.160 --> 05:08.600
Here.

05:12.959 --> 05:13.480
Sister Hui.

05:14.560 --> 05:16.360
I found another good quality in you.

05:17.319 --> 05:18.319
Besides Auntie's family,

05:18.360 --> 05:19.199
you take such good care of them.

05:19.560 --> 05:20.800
Auntie's friends

05:21.079 --> 05:22.680
are also treated so thoughtfully by you.

05:22.879 --> 05:24.199
Where can we find someone like you?

05:25.040 --> 05:26.120
Miss Xu.

05:27.120 --> 05:28.199
People like Ms. Meng

05:28.199 --> 05:29.920
aren't as easygoing as you.

05:30.360 --> 05:31.720
They're all so cunning.

05:32.120 --> 05:32.839
Sister Lan is always

05:32.839 --> 05:34.160
hanging out with them.

05:34.600 --> 05:36.040
If they say something bad about me,

05:36.079 --> 05:37.319
I could lose my job.

05:39.560 --> 05:40.439
But I think Auntie

05:40.480 --> 05:42.000
is a very independent person.

05:42.680 --> 05:44.160
Would she really listen to them?

05:48.639 --> 05:49.360
Miss Xu.

05:50.639 --> 05:52.279
I really think you're a good person.

05:52.319 --> 05:53.319
That's why I'm telling you this.

05:55.040 --> 05:56.079
In the past,

05:56.480 --> 05:57.800
someone introduced a girlfriend

05:57.839 --> 05:59.040
to Haoming.

05:59.800 --> 06:01.079
But that girl

06:01.600 --> 06:02.199
didn't win

06:02.199 --> 06:03.600
the ladies' favor.

06:03.839 --> 06:05.160
They all talked at once,

06:05.160 --> 06:06.360
criticizing her from all sides,

06:07.079 --> 06:08.560
and actually convinced Sister Lan.

06:08.839 --> 06:09.759
So Sister Lan

06:09.959 --> 06:11.480
rejected the girl.

06:13.199 --> 06:14.439
These aunties

06:15.240 --> 06:16.680
really have a lot of influence.

06:16.800 --> 06:17.959
Who doesn't agree?

06:18.480 --> 06:20.240
If they don't like someone,

06:20.319 --> 06:22.000
that person can't get into Sister Lan's circle.

06:22.360 --> 06:23.040
Let alone

06:23.199 --> 06:24.680
becoming Sister Lan's daughter-in-law.

06:30.560 --> 06:31.160
Sister Hui

06:32.160 --> 06:33.040
Wait for me a moment.

06:33.879 --> 06:34.879
Are two boxes enough?

06:38.879 --> 06:39.560
At this time,

06:39.600 --> 06:40.480
you have to eat cherries.

06:40.879 --> 06:41.879
I remember you told me

06:41.920 --> 06:42.839
you love cherries.

06:43.199 --> 06:44.160
I bought them for you.

06:44.800 --> 06:45.120
Let's go.

06:45.120 --> 06:46.759
These two boxes cost a few hundred yuan.

06:46.759 --> 06:47.480
I feel embarrassed.

06:47.480 --> 06:48.680
Take them home for the kids.

06:49.800 --> 06:50.959
Thank you so much.

06:53.279 --> 06:54.360
I forgot to buy shrimp.

06:54.839 --> 06:55.480
Let's go check out the shrimp.

06:55.519 --> 06:55.959
Okay.

07:01.240 --> 07:01.879
I know.

07:03.000 --> 07:03.920
Yu Lan and these people

07:03.959 --> 07:05.319
haven't truly accepted me.

07:07.279 --> 07:08.399
If I want to marry Hao Ming,

07:08.839 --> 07:10.600
I have to fully integrate into this family.

07:10.800 --> 07:11.639
This circle.

07:13.360 --> 07:14.319
What I can rely on

07:15.160 --> 07:16.639
is to take the initiative.

07:29.800 --> 07:30.560
Nice shot!

07:30.759 --> 07:31.600
Let's take a break.

07:35.920 --> 07:37.879
Sweating a bit today feels good.

07:38.000 --> 07:39.360
But it's actually a bit hot today.

07:39.800 --> 07:40.519
Right?

07:42.600 --> 07:43.199
Coach.

07:43.759 --> 07:44.959
Let's not be so strict today.

07:44.959 --> 07:45.360
Okay.

07:45.360 --> 07:46.480
Quick, wipe your sweat.

07:46.480 --> 07:46.800
Hurry.

07:46.959 --> 07:47.720
Seriously.

07:48.360 --> 07:49.120
It's really hot.

07:49.120 --> 07:50.600
Sister Lan is still as energetic as ever.

07:50.839 --> 07:51.519
Of course.

07:51.560 --> 07:53.480
All that daily yoga paid off.

08:09.360 --> 08:10.199
Did you invite her?

08:14.199 --> 08:14.720
Yes.

08:14.839 --> 08:15.959
She happened to be free today.

08:16.040 --> 08:17.439
I thought I'd bring her out to have some fun.

08:17.480 --> 08:19.079
To get to know each other better.

08:19.360 --> 08:20.519
But I didn't expect

08:20.680 --> 08:21.800
she can't play tennis.

08:22.839 --> 08:23.959
Have you met her parents?

08:25.600 --> 08:26.120
Yes, I have.

08:26.600 --> 08:27.720
They're intellectuals.

08:28.680 --> 08:29.879
They've lived abroad for many years.

08:30.560 --> 08:31.079
Her father

08:31.120 --> 08:32.600
is a professor at Syracuse University.

08:36.320 --> 08:37.799
No wonder she's so well-behaved.

08:38.480 --> 08:39.360
This girl

08:40.039 --> 08:41.039
is quite sensible.

08:42.679 --> 08:44.519
To join Sister Lan's family,

08:44.720 --> 08:46.120
you have to be sensible.

08:47.200 --> 08:48.559
I think this girl

08:48.639 --> 08:50.200
is low-key,

08:50.679 --> 08:51.960
but she's got depth.

08:57.600 --> 08:58.480
Xu,

08:58.960 --> 08:59.720
you don't have to rush.

08:59.720 --> 09:00.679
The coach

09:00.720 --> 09:01.559
will pick them up later.

09:01.720 --> 09:03.240
I just wanted to be quick.

09:03.559 --> 09:04.799
So you don't have to wait.

09:06.000 --> 09:06.720
Xu,

09:09.120 --> 09:10.240
you really don't have to do this.

09:10.519 --> 09:11.480
I think you're great.

09:12.000 --> 09:12.639
Relax a bit.

09:12.759 --> 09:14.320
No need to be so tense all the time.

09:14.960 --> 09:16.600
Sometimes, if you're too tense,

09:16.639 --> 09:17.919
it's not a good thing.

09:20.639 --> 09:21.879
Thank you, Sister Meiling.

09:25.440 --> 09:26.440
Sister Lan.

09:27.559 --> 09:28.679
Sister Meng, Sister Ma.

09:28.879 --> 09:30.120
What a coincidence!

09:30.360 --> 09:31.679
You're here too.

09:32.960 --> 09:33.679
Sister Meng,

09:33.879 --> 09:34.759
since I last saw you,

09:34.759 --> 09:35.840
you've lost weight again.

09:37.120 --> 09:38.200
Not really.

09:38.559 --> 09:39.159
Really.

09:39.240 --> 09:40.200
You've lost quite a bit.

09:40.320 --> 09:41.320
I've been accompanying my husband lately,

09:41.399 --> 09:42.080
attending

09:42.080 --> 09:43.279
several thank-you banquets.

09:43.480 --> 09:44.519
Stayed up late for a few days.

09:44.559 --> 09:45.320
I've actually gained a few kilos.

09:45.320 --> 09:46.039
Really?

09:46.159 --> 09:47.360
You can't tell at all.

09:47.440 --> 09:48.120
Right? Really?

09:48.120 --> 09:49.039
Can't see it, can't see it.

09:49.360 --> 09:49.759
Everyone knows

09:49.759 --> 09:50.840
you're your husband's

09:50.840 --> 09:51.840
social expert.

09:52.080 --> 09:53.519
If it weren't for your ladies' gatherings,

09:53.600 --> 09:54.840
how could he have met Old Zheng

09:54.840 --> 09:56.240
and landed Shifeng's biggest project?

09:57.840 --> 09:58.600
That's just

09:58.679 --> 09:59.559
my regular job.

09:59.639 --> 10:00.559
Unlike you,

10:00.840 --> 10:02.440
your husband and son are so outstanding.

10:02.720 --> 10:04.240
I'm just destined to worry.

10:04.759 --> 10:06.679
Haven't I been the same lately?

10:06.960 --> 10:08.240
Let me tell you, lately

10:08.279 --> 10:09.799
I've been going to the gym every day.

10:10.200 --> 10:11.120
My husband

10:11.159 --> 10:12.559
is doing business with the president of Boyue Group.

10:12.559 --> 10:13.240
They're negotiating deals.

10:13.399 --> 10:14.879
The president's wife

10:14.879 --> 10:16.039
is a fashion designer.

10:16.279 --> 10:17.000
So to get closer to her,

10:17.000 --> 10:17.840
I have to get closer.

10:18.080 --> 10:19.080
I have to fit myself into

10:19.080 --> 10:20.840
the clothes she designs.

10:22.679 --> 10:24.039
You're working so hard for your husband.

10:24.159 --> 10:25.559
Your year-end bonus should go up this year.

10:26.240 --> 10:28.320
Sister Lan, what are you saying?

10:29.639 --> 10:30.600
Let me tell you,

10:30.720 --> 10:32.039
a wife who's good at socializing

10:32.240 --> 10:33.840
makes her husband's business twice as effective.

10:33.919 --> 10:35.159
Unlike those bachelors

10:35.200 --> 10:36.519
who only focus on their careers.

10:36.639 --> 10:37.480
They're capable too,

10:37.639 --> 10:39.360
but without a wife's support,

10:39.440 --> 10:40.799
it's like missing a leg.

10:40.840 --> 10:41.720
They can't go far.

10:42.320 --> 10:43.720
Do you remember the last gathering?

10:43.840 --> 10:44.600
President Qu showed up.

10:55.480 --> 10:56.279
Ms. Qu is here.

10:56.360 --> 10:57.720
Ms. Qu, you finally made it.

10:57.759 --> 10:59.120
We've been waiting for you, Ms. Qu.

10:59.159 --> 11:00.159
We didn't dare start without you.

11:00.200 --> 11:01.200
You can play without me.

11:01.399 --> 11:01.879
Have a seat, please.

11:01.879 --> 11:02.480
Ms. Qu.

11:02.480 --> 11:03.960
Since I last saw you,

11:03.960 --> 11:05.240
your skin looks so much better.

11:05.399 --> 11:06.360
Really.

11:07.279 --> 11:08.360
You look healthier too.

11:09.799 --> 11:10.639
By the way, Ms. Qu,

11:10.840 --> 11:11.720
I heard your husband, Mr. Xiao,

11:11.759 --> 11:12.879
has taken on many big projects.

11:14.000 --> 11:15.320
He just can't sit still.

11:15.559 --> 11:16.360
I've told him too,

11:16.679 --> 11:18.000
you can't make all the money in the world.

11:20.080 --> 11:20.679
Ms. Qu,

11:21.039 --> 11:22.320
can you ask Mr. Xiao

11:22.440 --> 11:24.000
to help our Mr. Feng too?

11:24.600 --> 11:24.960
Let's go.

11:25.039 --> 11:25.559
Let's play first.

11:25.600 --> 11:26.480
Come on, let's go.

11:26.720 --> 11:27.200
Let's go.

11:32.720 --> 11:33.720
Coach, I need a break.

11:33.720 --> 11:34.360
Give it to me, I can't go on.

11:35.519 --> 11:36.360
Thanks, Xu.

11:36.399 --> 11:37.000
No problem.

11:39.919 --> 11:40.600
Have some water.

11:42.039 --> 11:42.720
Thank you.

11:44.519 --> 11:45.679
Who's that?

11:46.240 --> 11:48.080
That's a director from Blue Fir Capital.

11:48.279 --> 11:49.679
She's also Mr. Xiao's wife.

11:50.519 --> 11:51.600
Blue Fir Capital, huh?

11:51.679 --> 11:52.679
They're really hot right now.

11:53.639 --> 11:55.159
Everyone wants to get to her

11:55.200 --> 11:56.519
to get resources for their husbands.

11:58.399 --> 11:59.120
Impressive.

12:01.159 --> 12:02.639
She's the center of attention.

12:02.759 --> 12:03.919
She's so full of herself.

12:05.159 --> 12:06.200
A while ago,

12:06.240 --> 12:07.440
I asked a friend to set up a meeting with her.

12:08.080 --> 12:09.360
But she acted all high and mighty.

12:09.679 --> 12:10.360
She didn't come.

12:55.799 --> 12:56.799
Let's go.

12:57.000 --> 13:01.519
Two, two, three, four.

13:02.120 --> 13:02.879
One.

13:03.320 --> 13:04.120
Two.

13:04.600 --> 13:05.679
Three.

13:16.279 --> 13:16.840
Not bad.

13:16.840 --> 13:18.039
You danced really well today.

13:18.679 --> 13:19.600
Let's try another one today.

13:19.600 --> 13:20.440
A new water sleeve move.

13:20.440 --> 13:21.039
Okay, okay.

13:21.440 --> 13:22.399
Watch my demonstration.

13:24.679 --> 13:25.279
See that?

13:25.399 --> 13:26.279
It's two flowers.

13:26.559 --> 13:27.440
One on top,

13:27.559 --> 13:28.360
one below.

13:28.440 --> 13:29.879
These two make one flower.

13:30.080 --> 13:30.759
Like this, one on top,

13:30.799 --> 13:31.399
one below.

13:31.440 --> 13:32.360
Yes, try it.

13:32.919 --> 13:34.879
One on top, one below.

13:35.320 --> 13:35.879
Just...

13:36.080 --> 13:36.519
Still...

13:36.519 --> 13:37.279
This is too big.

13:37.279 --> 13:38.200
Watch mine.

13:39.039 --> 13:39.519
Like this.

13:40.879 --> 13:42.200
I heard from a friend

13:42.639 --> 13:43.559
that Ms. Qu

13:43.639 --> 13:44.919
doesn't have any other hobbies,

13:45.279 --> 13:47.440
she's just obsessed with Kunqu Opera.

13:47.879 --> 13:48.960
She even pays out of her own pocket

13:48.960 --> 13:50.080
to organize Kunqu Opera

13:50.120 --> 13:51.159
enthusiasts competitions.

13:55.360 --> 13:57.240
One up, one down.

13:57.240 --> 13:57.879
No.

13:58.519 --> 13:59.360
It's okay, take your time.

14:03.320 --> 14:03.960
Let me try, let me try.

14:03.960 --> 14:04.879
This is harder than I thought.

14:04.960 --> 14:05.840
It is a bit difficult.

14:06.039 --> 14:06.720
Here, look.

14:07.200 --> 14:08.960
One, two.

14:09.159 --> 14:10.480
One, two, yes.

14:10.879 --> 14:11.399
Today

14:11.399 --> 14:12.639
is our first class.

14:12.679 --> 14:13.279
So,

14:13.320 --> 14:14.679
let's start with the basics

14:14.679 --> 14:15.600
and practice from there.

14:15.720 --> 14:17.000
Excuse me, teacher,

14:17.360 --> 14:18.039
sorry to interrupt.

14:19.600 --> 14:20.960
Can you teach me directly

14:21.399 --> 14:22.039
the water sleeves

14:22.639 --> 14:23.559
and the water sleeve flower?

14:24.759 --> 14:26.200
Haste makes waste.

14:26.320 --> 14:27.519
As a beginner,

14:27.559 --> 14:28.919
I suggest we start

14:28.960 --> 14:29.799
with the basics.

14:30.919 --> 14:31.960
Then let me ask,

14:33.000 --> 14:34.759
even if I don't eat or sleep,

14:35.159 --> 14:36.480
how long will it take to master it?

14:36.840 --> 14:37.960
At the fastest, at least a month.

14:38.039 --> 14:38.679
So let's

14:38.679 --> 14:40.039
start with the basics.

14:40.159 --> 14:41.000
The water sleeve flower

14:41.000 --> 14:41.840
can wait.

14:42.440 --> 14:42.919
No.

14:44.960 --> 14:46.080
I only want to practice the water sleeve flower.

14:48.240 --> 14:50.039
For water sleeves, we need to pay attention

14:50.080 --> 14:50.840
to this part.

14:51.039 --> 14:52.360
Don't use your upper arm.

14:52.360 --> 14:54.799
Use your wrist and forearm strength.

14:55.120 --> 14:56.399
When switching sides,

14:56.679 --> 14:57.159
it's

14:57.320 --> 14:58.960
one flower up, one flower down.

14:59.000 --> 15:00.360
One up, one down.

15:00.720 --> 15:01.080
Right.

15:01.159 --> 15:02.720
Keep them flat.

15:03.559 --> 15:05.000
During this process, your upper arm

15:05.200 --> 15:06.600
shouldn't use much force.

15:07.120 --> 15:08.600
Same with both hands.

15:09.080 --> 15:11.000
Look, the upper arms barely move.

15:11.279 --> 15:13.240
It's all in the forearms and wrists.

15:13.960 --> 15:15.120
Then, turn.

15:16.240 --> 15:18.440
Up and down, up and down.

15:19.279 --> 15:20.039
You try it.

15:22.440 --> 15:24.080
Use your forearm and wrist.

15:24.120 --> 15:24.639
Swing it like this.

15:24.679 --> 15:25.600
Yes, go.

15:40.960 --> 15:41.679
Up and down.

15:58.720 --> 15:59.240
Sis,

15:59.360 --> 16:00.960
all departments are almost ready.

16:01.159 --> 16:01.639
Okay.

16:01.799 --> 16:02.799
Let's check the script one more time.

16:02.840 --> 16:03.919
Then we can start recording.

16:04.440 --> 16:05.080
Sis,

16:05.639 --> 16:06.440
what are you doing?

16:11.080 --> 16:12.440
It's my tendonitis.

16:12.960 --> 16:14.200
Typing too much does this.

16:14.360 --> 16:14.960
Alright, come on.

16:14.960 --> 16:15.600
Let's get ready.

16:15.720 --> 16:16.320
Get ready.

16:16.360 --> 16:16.919
Go ahead.

16:17.039 --> 16:18.120
Okay, let's get started.

16:18.960 --> 16:20.039
Ready to begin.

16:33.879 --> 16:35.279
You did really well in practice today.

16:35.600 --> 16:36.440
Go home and get some rest.

16:36.480 --> 16:37.639
That's it for today's class.

16:38.519 --> 16:39.240
Teacher.

16:39.639 --> 16:40.360
Can I stay here

16:40.360 --> 16:41.000
and practice a bit longer?

16:41.159 --> 16:41.679
Sure.

16:41.759 --> 16:42.879
No one else has class after this.

16:42.919 --> 16:43.639
You can keep practicing.

16:43.840 --> 16:44.279
Thank you.

16:51.600 --> 16:53.279
Can't you take a break for once?

16:53.360 --> 16:54.440
That's different.

16:55.559 --> 16:57.960
Kunqu Opera is all about posture

16:58.799 --> 16:59.799
and technique.

16:59.879 --> 17:01.200
You really have to practice a lot.

17:03.080 --> 17:03.559
By the way,

17:04.000 --> 17:05.759
the follow-up from the hospital

17:05.799 --> 17:07.079
came back.

17:07.240 --> 17:09.079
Your cholesterol is still a bit high.

17:09.200 --> 17:10.559
So I bought you some fish oil.

17:10.640 --> 17:11.400
Take it three times a day.

17:11.519 --> 17:13.200
Take it half an hour before meals.

17:13.240 --> 17:13.839
You have to remember,

17:13.880 --> 17:14.680
take it every day.

17:16.279 --> 17:16.759
Okay.

17:17.279 --> 17:18.440
Send it to me by courier.

17:19.960 --> 17:20.559
I already sent

17:20.559 --> 17:21.680
everything to you by courier.

17:21.880 --> 17:22.640
Remember to pick it up.

17:23.720 --> 17:24.200
Alright.

17:25.319 --> 17:26.559
How's your Kunqu Opera practice

17:26.559 --> 17:27.640
going?

17:28.319 --> 17:29.279
Did your teacher say

17:29.400 --> 17:30.720
how you're doing?

17:31.640 --> 17:32.920
The teacher praised me.

17:32.920 --> 17:34.119
Said I learn quickly.

17:35.119 --> 17:36.559
I have to thank you for that.

17:36.759 --> 17:38.119
You always told me as a kid

17:38.440 --> 17:40.319
to learn as many skills as possible.

17:40.480 --> 17:42.119
The more skills, the better.

17:42.400 --> 17:43.640
That's why the teacher praised me.

17:44.000 --> 17:45.000
Right?

17:45.240 --> 17:47.599
Listening to Grandma's advice is always right.

17:47.680 --> 17:49.240
Listen to Grandma's advice.

17:51.880 --> 17:53.279
Grandma wants to ask you,

17:53.400 --> 17:55.480
do you have time to come visit?

17:57.720 --> 17:58.720
Once I

18:00.400 --> 18:01.519
finish up this busy period,

18:01.960 --> 18:02.640
After I'm done with work,

18:02.640 --> 18:03.720
I'll come back and spend time with you.

18:04.359 --> 18:05.559
I also bought you

18:05.599 --> 18:06.880
a set of Kunqu Opera costumes.

18:07.119 --> 18:08.319
When I get back, I'll teach you

18:08.480 --> 18:09.319
and we can practice together.

18:11.200 --> 18:12.920
Alright, you go ahead and work.

18:13.119 --> 18:14.319
Grandma's going to sleep now.

18:15.039 --> 18:16.240
Okay, rest early.

18:16.279 --> 18:17.440
It's already late.

18:18.000 --> 18:19.279
Go to bed early. Good night.

19:01.839 --> 19:03.079
Remember to use your waist.

19:04.319 --> 19:05.119
Side waist.

19:05.279 --> 19:06.480
Watch your hands.

19:06.559 --> 19:07.319
Strike a pose.

19:07.480 --> 19:08.599
Finish with your waist.

19:09.039 --> 19:09.599
Yes.

19:09.880 --> 19:10.480
That's right.

19:11.799 --> 19:12.160
Good.

19:12.319 --> 19:12.720
Very good.

19:12.880 --> 19:14.200
That's all for today's class.

19:14.400 --> 19:15.640
Go home and rest early.

19:16.160 --> 19:16.599
Teacher.

19:16.680 --> 19:17.200
I know.

19:17.440 --> 19:18.039
I'll practice a bit more.

19:18.240 --> 19:18.720
Okay.

19:18.799 --> 19:19.200
Bye.

19:19.200 --> 19:19.720
Thank you.

19:26.480 --> 19:27.119
Teacher.

19:28.039 --> 19:29.440
Is this girl new?

19:29.440 --> 19:30.480
I haven't seen her before.

19:30.559 --> 19:31.480
Yes, she just joined.

19:31.759 --> 19:32.559
She's pretty smart.

19:32.680 --> 19:33.759
She got this good after just a few days.

19:39.359 --> 19:40.079
Hello.

19:41.640 --> 19:42.119
Hello.

19:42.160 --> 19:43.960
I saw your water sleeves moves.

19:44.480 --> 19:45.599
They're really good.

19:45.720 --> 19:46.400
Thank you.

19:46.799 --> 19:47.680
I heard from the teacher

19:47.680 --> 19:48.960
that you just started learning?

19:49.720 --> 19:51.319
I've liked it since I was a kid.

19:51.920 --> 19:53.680
I thought it looked beautiful back then.

19:54.640 --> 19:55.720
Now that I'm grown up,

19:56.119 --> 19:57.759
I can really appreciate its charm.

19:58.240 --> 19:59.319
So I decided to study it properly.

20:00.079 --> 20:01.000
That's rare.

20:01.480 --> 20:03.359
So young and already into Kunqu Opera.

20:03.640 --> 20:05.359
Me too, I've loved it since I was little.

20:05.880 --> 20:06.559
Recently,

20:06.559 --> 20:08.400
we're having a Kunqu Opera Enthusiasts Competition.

20:08.920 --> 20:10.079
I'm the organizer.

20:10.319 --> 20:11.160
I was thinking,

20:11.359 --> 20:12.519
as the organizer,

20:12.720 --> 20:13.880
if I can't perform a piece,

20:13.920 --> 20:14.920
people will laugh at me.

20:15.119 --> 20:16.599
So I'm here for some last-minute practice.

20:17.079 --> 20:17.839
Let me introduce myself.

20:18.240 --> 20:19.160
I'm Qu Li.

20:20.559 --> 20:21.440
Hello, Sister Li.

20:22.440 --> 20:23.160
I'm Xu Yan.

20:23.599 --> 20:24.799
You seem so talented.

20:25.000 --> 20:26.160
You should join our competition.

20:26.160 --> 20:26.880
Come and have fun.

20:27.119 --> 20:27.759
No problem.

20:28.640 --> 20:29.680
That's great!

20:30.480 --> 20:31.640
The teacher's already left.

20:31.839 --> 20:32.880
Why don't we practice together?

20:32.920 --> 20:34.200
Help me get the feel for it.

20:34.680 --> 20:35.279
That would be great.

20:35.319 --> 20:36.559
I was just about to take a break.

20:36.960 --> 20:37.799
Let me take a look for you.

20:38.000 --> 20:39.680
My water sleeves

20:40.319 --> 20:41.599
just won't spin properly.

20:41.640 --> 20:43.240
Can you see what's wrong?

20:43.279 --> 20:44.000
Yeah, look.

20:44.039 --> 20:45.359
I can't do it like you.

20:45.839 --> 20:46.759
You just need to

20:47.359 --> 20:48.640
keep a bit of distance

20:48.640 --> 20:49.640
between your sleeves and your body.

20:49.720 --> 20:51.079
Like this, toss them out a bit.

20:51.279 --> 20:52.279
Toss them, just a little.

20:52.279 --> 20:52.720
Yes.

20:52.960 --> 20:54.440
Let them go out and then bring them back.

20:54.559 --> 20:55.039
Right.

20:55.440 --> 20:55.880
Yes.

20:55.960 --> 20:56.920
Keep some space between your hands and your body.

20:56.920 --> 20:57.920
There should be a gap.

20:58.240 --> 20:58.720
That's right.

20:58.759 --> 20:59.359
Like this.

20:59.559 --> 21:00.519
Then you can swing them properly.

21:01.480 --> 21:02.119
Exactly.

21:03.720 --> 21:04.319
That's it.

21:04.400 --> 21:05.960
You really know how to focus on the key points.

21:06.839 --> 21:07.599
That's it.

21:29.640 --> 21:30.720
Let me take this call first.

21:30.759 --> 21:31.119
Okay.

21:35.599 --> 21:36.319
Old Zhao.

21:38.240 --> 21:38.839
Yes.

21:39.000 --> 21:39.799
That's the one.

21:41.079 --> 21:42.119
Rhine International School.

21:42.200 --> 21:42.559
Right.

21:45.400 --> 21:46.559
Isn't it for Haohao?

21:49.759 --> 21:50.319
Over there,

21:50.319 --> 21:52.000
they really don't have a single spot available?

21:54.720 --> 21:55.480
Alright, alright.

22:01.599 --> 22:03.119
You must have some basics.

22:03.160 --> 22:04.440
With your posture,

22:04.799 --> 22:05.920
you must have learned dance.

22:06.440 --> 22:07.559
I haven't learned dance.

22:08.119 --> 22:09.200
Actually, I'm a host.

22:09.599 --> 22:11.039
You're a host?

22:11.160 --> 22:12.079
What do you host?

22:12.599 --> 22:13.119
Family Banquet.

22:13.359 --> 22:14.039
Have you seen it?

22:15.599 --> 22:16.480
I think I really

22:16.480 --> 22:17.440
have seen your show.

22:17.480 --> 22:18.799
Are there a lot of celebrities

22:18.799 --> 22:19.720
cooking together?

22:19.920 --> 22:20.480
That's right.

22:21.039 --> 22:21.759
But now,

22:21.799 --> 22:23.200
the program's plan has been revamped.

22:23.519 --> 22:24.880
We're planning to invite

22:24.960 --> 22:26.599
influential women from various fields

22:26.960 --> 22:27.519
to participate.

22:30.279 --> 22:30.880
Sorry.

22:31.319 --> 22:32.279
I have something else to do.

22:32.480 --> 22:33.119
I'll leave now.

22:46.920 --> 22:47.759
Qu Li.

22:48.279 --> 22:49.319
She'll really come?

22:50.880 --> 22:51.799
Of course.

22:52.799 --> 22:54.440
That's why I'm here to invite you.

22:54.640 --> 22:56.200
Do I have to go on Family Banquet?

22:57.160 --> 22:58.119
Xu Yan.

22:58.799 --> 23:00.799
If President Qu comes, I'll definitely be there.

23:02.319 --> 23:03.119
Sister Meiling.

23:03.359 --> 23:05.519
I have a list of potential guests here.

23:05.839 --> 23:07.359
See if there's anyone you know.

23:07.799 --> 23:09.000
If we record the show,

23:09.200 --> 23:10.559
having familiar friends

23:11.000 --> 23:11.960
will make the atmosphere better.

23:12.480 --> 23:13.319
Xu Yan,

23:13.960 --> 23:15.359
it's good you came to ask me.

23:15.680 --> 23:16.359
You know,

23:16.559 --> 23:17.920
among these people,

23:18.119 --> 23:19.119
there's a lot of discord.

23:21.000 --> 23:22.240
Let me explain it to you in detail.

23:46.720 --> 23:47.880
You want to change the guests?

23:47.920 --> 23:48.359
Yes.

23:49.200 --> 23:50.480
This is the new proposal.

23:58.799 --> 24:00.240
Xiao Nanpeng's wife,

24:00.519 --> 24:01.400
Blue Fir Capital,

24:01.599 --> 24:03.079
Global Managing Partner.

24:04.480 --> 24:05.559
I've already invited her.

24:05.559 --> 24:06.759
For our next episode.

24:08.519 --> 24:09.680
What about the other guests?

24:10.240 --> 24:11.519
President Qu has already been invited.

24:12.079 --> 24:12.839
I think

24:13.000 --> 24:14.640
female representatives from other industries

24:15.279 --> 24:16.400
shouldn't be a problem.

24:20.640 --> 24:21.440
Director Zhou.

24:21.640 --> 24:22.319
Our show

24:22.359 --> 24:23.319
has been running for three years.

24:24.480 --> 24:25.119
Right now,

24:25.160 --> 24:26.519
celebrities are no longer interested

24:26.519 --> 24:27.599
in our type of show.

24:28.519 --> 24:30.799
Audience interest also needs to be boosted.

24:31.880 --> 24:34.279
Besides keeping celebrity guests,

24:34.720 --> 24:36.359
we can also invite

24:36.640 --> 24:38.640
influential people from various fields

24:38.640 --> 24:39.319
to join.

24:39.720 --> 24:41.359
It might spark something new.

24:42.200 --> 24:43.720
As long as the show is good enough,

24:44.240 --> 24:45.319
those who watch it

24:46.519 --> 24:48.119
will probably want to come.

24:48.519 --> 24:49.880
That's a great idea.

24:50.480 --> 24:51.200
I support it.

24:52.920 --> 24:54.160
But I have one condition.

24:56.480 --> 24:58.000
My application to switch to host

24:59.559 --> 25:00.240
please

25:00.519 --> 25:01.480
submit it again.

25:05.920 --> 25:06.839
I'll give you this chance.

25:07.799 --> 25:08.680
Go ahead and do it.

25:11.640 --> 25:12.440
Thank you, Director.

25:25.359 --> 25:26.000
Sister Li.

25:26.799 --> 25:27.480
I know

25:27.880 --> 25:28.920
you're not interested

25:28.960 --> 25:30.119
in joining the show at all.

25:30.599 --> 25:31.799
Then why did you come to me?

25:32.279 --> 25:33.319
What if it's a show

25:33.839 --> 25:35.720
tailored just for you?

25:40.119 --> 25:42.000
The director of Rhine International School

25:43.519 --> 25:44.240
will also be there.

25:45.319 --> 25:46.160
You're investigating me.

25:47.759 --> 25:48.839
Just trying to help you out.

25:50.799 --> 25:51.640
Even without you,

25:51.720 --> 25:52.960
I can still meet them.

25:54.759 --> 25:55.880
With your abilities,

25:56.680 --> 25:58.119
of course you can meet these people.

25:58.519 --> 26:00.359
But to quickly build relationships

26:01.119 --> 26:02.200
isn't that easy.

26:02.799 --> 26:04.319
If it's through a show,

26:04.599 --> 26:05.559
it can naturally

26:05.559 --> 26:06.599
turn into friendships.

26:07.359 --> 26:08.480
It's all benefit, no harm.

26:10.200 --> 26:10.720
Isn't it?

26:12.839 --> 26:13.720
Unfortunately,

26:14.279 --> 26:15.240
I can't cook.

26:16.039 --> 26:16.960
As the initiator of the Kunqu Opera Competition,

26:17.000 --> 26:18.079
with that identity,

26:18.119 --> 26:19.240
wouldn't it be better?

26:22.519 --> 26:23.680
If you join this episode of Family Banquet,

26:24.200 --> 26:26.240
I'll specially plan

26:26.319 --> 26:27.880
a Kunqu Opera showcase for you.

26:28.480 --> 26:29.920
By participating in this episode,

26:30.279 --> 26:30.920
you can not only

26:30.920 --> 26:32.319
promote the Kunqu Opera Competition,

26:32.799 --> 26:34.079
but also make

26:34.200 --> 26:35.519
like-minded friends.

26:36.519 --> 26:37.640
More importantly,

26:38.200 --> 26:39.559
once the show airs,

26:39.720 --> 26:41.359
many more people

26:41.559 --> 26:43.039
will experience the charm of Kunqu Opera.

26:43.599 --> 26:44.240
You've loved

26:44.240 --> 26:45.640
Kunqu Opera for most of your life.

26:46.519 --> 26:47.720
This must be what you want to do.

26:50.640 --> 26:51.440
Also,

26:52.680 --> 26:54.240
the Kunqu Opera Enthusiasts Competition,

26:55.359 --> 26:56.400
I'm willing to host it

26:56.400 --> 26:57.480
for you for free.

26:58.079 --> 26:59.240
But I don't know

27:00.119 --> 27:01.519
if I'll have that honor.

27:25.440 --> 27:26.920
Thank you so much, Sister Li.

27:27.000 --> 27:29.039
For using traditional Chinese opera style

27:29.039 --> 27:29.480
Kunqu Opera

27:29.720 --> 27:30.799
to bring us

27:30.799 --> 27:31.880
such a wonderful opening.

27:35.240 --> 27:36.480
First, let me introduce

27:36.480 --> 27:38.160
today's new guests.

27:38.839 --> 27:39.960
The famous film and television actress,

27:40.000 --> 27:41.160
Ms. Xue Yuqing.

27:41.480 --> 27:42.000
Hello, everyone.

27:42.000 --> 27:43.640
I'm actress Xue Yuqing.

27:43.799 --> 27:44.880
Welcome to the show.

27:45.279 --> 27:46.680
National Senior Public Nutritionist,

27:46.799 --> 27:47.960
Ms. He Jingshu.

27:48.079 --> 27:48.920
Hello, everyone.

27:49.039 --> 27:50.880
Director of Rhine International School,

27:51.039 --> 27:52.319
Ms. An Yaqin.

27:54.720 --> 27:57.119
And young female entrepreneur,

27:57.519 --> 27:58.599
Ms. Sun Meiling.

27:58.680 --> 27:59.799
Welcome to all of you.

28:00.079 --> 28:00.559
By the way,

28:01.279 --> 28:02.200
Ms. Yuqing,

28:02.319 --> 28:04.440
I heard your new drama

28:04.640 --> 28:05.759
is very popular right now.

28:06.119 --> 28:07.359
The character you play

28:07.359 --> 28:09.079
is a strong-willed

28:09.119 --> 28:10.119
female imperial chef, right?

28:11.079 --> 28:12.559
So, in your memory,

28:14.200 --> 28:15.440
which dish impressed you the most?

28:15.440 --> 28:16.079
What is it?

28:18.000 --> 28:19.160
Qianlong Cabbage.

28:19.319 --> 28:20.880
Cherry Braised Pork.

28:21.039 --> 28:22.680
And Braised Deer Tendon, and others.

28:22.839 --> 28:23.680
When you actually take part

28:23.720 --> 28:25.400
in making these dishes,

28:25.559 --> 28:26.359
you realize

28:26.519 --> 28:27.519
the craftsmanship,

28:27.599 --> 28:28.559
the precision,

28:28.680 --> 28:30.160
and everything about it

28:30.200 --> 28:31.079
shows

28:31.400 --> 28:32.480
it's truly

28:32.599 --> 28:34.799
perfect in color, aroma, taste, meaning, and appearance.

28:35.480 --> 28:36.680
Well said!

28:37.359 --> 28:37.880
Sister Li,

28:38.319 --> 28:39.920
your husband is known in the industry

28:39.960 --> 28:42.440
as the "Iron Man of Business."

28:42.640 --> 28:44.599
He often works around the clock.

28:45.279 --> 28:46.880
Taking care of such a partner

28:47.000 --> 28:48.519
must take a lot of effort.

28:48.839 --> 28:49.759
So I'd like to ask,

28:50.000 --> 28:51.680
what dish do you cook most often at home?

28:51.680 --> 28:52.279
What is it?

28:52.759 --> 28:55.000
Mr. Xiao is indeed very busy with work.

28:55.799 --> 28:56.759
So when it comes to meals,

28:56.799 --> 28:59.039
we always keep it quick and simple.

28:59.319 --> 29:00.680
If you ask what I cook most,

29:01.519 --> 29:02.799
it's usually staple foods.

29:02.960 --> 29:05.480
Sometimes with light porridge and small dishes.

29:05.559 --> 29:06.680
As mentioned earlier,

29:06.799 --> 29:08.119
Qianlong Cabbage

29:08.200 --> 29:09.920
is also Mr. Xiao's favorite.

29:11.119 --> 29:12.480
So it's Qianlong Cabbage.

29:13.000 --> 29:14.799
Why don't we have a live

29:14.920 --> 29:16.359
cooking competition, shall we?

29:16.480 --> 29:19.160
Let's have Sister Li and Ms. Yuqing

29:19.359 --> 29:20.519
both make Qianlong Cabbage.

29:20.640 --> 29:21.960
Let's see who makes it more authentic.

29:25.000 --> 29:25.759
Sister Meiling,

29:26.519 --> 29:28.079
I've heard your cooking skills

29:28.079 --> 29:29.039
are also excellent.

29:29.880 --> 29:31.039
My husband especially loves

29:31.039 --> 29:31.720
the food I make.

29:31.759 --> 29:32.359
So,

29:32.359 --> 29:33.839
I cook for him at home every day.

29:34.960 --> 29:36.720
Let me help divide everyone into groups.

29:37.640 --> 29:38.319
Sister Meiling,

29:38.640 --> 29:40.559
you and Sister Li

29:40.599 --> 29:41.559
and Ms. Yaqin are one team.

29:42.160 --> 29:43.720
I'll team up with Ms. Jingshu

29:43.799 --> 29:44.640
and Ms. Yuqing.

29:44.680 --> 29:45.200
Is that okay?

29:45.240 --> 29:46.039
Great!

29:47.039 --> 29:48.079
Let's move over to

29:48.079 --> 29:49.200
our Family Banquet kitchen.

29:49.240 --> 29:50.160
Many of my friends are at

29:50.160 --> 29:50.960
Rhine School.

29:51.240 --> 29:52.680
They all say the school atmosphere is excellent.

29:52.960 --> 29:54.160
This is the finest

29:54.359 --> 29:56.039
and most delicate cabbage I've ever seen.

29:56.200 --> 29:57.559
I learned this while filming.

29:57.839 --> 29:59.079
Do you need any help?

29:59.119 --> 30:00.039
Not at the moment.

30:00.160 --> 30:01.720
You can watch for now.

30:01.759 --> 30:02.759
Should we add honey first?

30:02.880 --> 30:03.559
Yes, definitely.

30:03.599 --> 30:04.920
Honey is the key.

30:05.599 --> 30:06.480
No wonder.

30:06.640 --> 30:08.079
I never added it before.

30:08.079 --> 30:08.839
That's why the taste was off.

30:09.200 --> 30:10.680
Let's see how they're doing over there.

30:10.799 --> 30:12.039
Making Qianlong Cabbage

30:12.119 --> 30:13.000
never tastes quite right.

30:14.200 --> 30:14.880
What's going on?

30:15.000 --> 30:15.599
Someone's here to steal

30:15.599 --> 30:17.319
our secret ingredient!

30:17.799 --> 30:18.440
Sister Yuqing,

30:18.920 --> 30:19.519
Ms. Jingshu,

30:19.599 --> 30:20.920
they're sneaking honey in over here.

30:21.599 --> 30:22.240
It's fine.

30:22.359 --> 30:23.480
We have our own secret recipe too.

30:23.759 --> 30:24.920
Don't copy us!

30:25.000 --> 30:26.440
This is Sister Li's special recipe.

30:26.440 --> 30:27.480
It looks pretty good on camera.

30:39.440 --> 30:40.200
Meiling

30:40.880 --> 30:42.319
Your husband is in Wenzhou

30:42.480 --> 30:43.799
planning to build a hot spring club

30:44.079 --> 30:46.279
He’s been wanting to talk to Lao Xiao about investment

30:46.519 --> 30:47.440
Now you’re helping him

30:47.440 --> 30:48.599
He’s met Qu Li

30:48.880 --> 30:49.920
That’s a big achievement

30:50.319 --> 30:51.359
Looks like

30:51.680 --> 30:53.640
the year-end bonus is coming early

30:55.440 --> 30:56.480
You mean this?

30:57.559 --> 30:58.440
Just a small reward

30:58.880 --> 30:59.680
Year-end bonus

30:59.839 --> 31:00.920
Shouldn’t there be something big?

31:04.200 --> 31:04.799
Stop looking

31:04.880 --> 31:05.920
Let’s chat for a bit

31:06.359 --> 31:07.440
Look at me

31:07.640 --> 31:08.960
I’m not photogenic, too chubby

31:09.039 --> 31:09.880
It’s fine

31:10.240 --> 31:10.960
Pretty good

31:11.200 --> 31:12.640
If you say it’s fine, it must be

31:13.680 --> 31:14.599
Miss Xu

31:15.319 --> 31:17.720
Your show is quite interesting

31:18.519 --> 31:19.720
Thank you, Auntie Ma

31:21.200 --> 31:23.119
The next Family Banquet episode

31:23.200 --> 31:24.680
President Qu will still attend

31:25.559 --> 31:27.640
Not sure if Auntie Ma and Auntie Meng

31:27.799 --> 31:28.839
have time

31:29.200 --> 31:30.200
Auntie Yu said

31:30.480 --> 31:32.079
She reserved spots for both of you

31:34.160 --> 31:35.599
Sister Lan

31:36.039 --> 31:38.119
Why are you so good to us?

31:39.039 --> 31:39.880
Thank you

31:40.279 --> 31:41.039
Of course

31:41.039 --> 31:42.319
With such a good opportunity

31:42.519 --> 31:43.880
I think of my sisters first

31:44.279 --> 31:45.119
So, the next episode

31:45.119 --> 31:46.000
When is it?

31:46.519 --> 31:47.319
Monday

31:48.039 --> 31:48.720
Monday

31:49.400 --> 31:50.599
That’s just a few days away

31:52.000 --> 31:52.799
I’ll head back first

31:53.000 --> 31:53.559
Get my hair done

31:55.079 --> 31:57.000
I need to get a facial too

31:57.039 --> 31:57.559
And get my nails done

31:57.599 --> 31:58.839
I get it, I get it

31:59.160 --> 32:00.039
Alright, Sister Lan

32:00.039 --> 32:00.799
Thanks

32:00.920 --> 32:01.559
I’ll leave now

32:01.680 --> 32:02.000
Bye

32:02.000 --> 32:02.720
See you Monday, Auntie Meng

32:02.720 --> 32:03.119
Bye

32:03.119 --> 32:03.880
See you Monday, Auntie Ma

32:03.960 --> 32:04.799
Thank you, see you Monday

32:06.359 --> 32:07.240
Xu

32:10.079 --> 32:11.519
For the next episode

32:11.680 --> 32:12.480
Am I still going?

32:14.279 --> 32:15.599
Of course

32:15.960 --> 32:16.960
Auntie Yu said

32:17.039 --> 32:18.559
You stand out on TV

32:19.960 --> 32:20.839
Then I really need to go back

32:20.839 --> 32:22.480
and get myself ready

32:22.599 --> 32:23.359
I won’t chat with you now

32:23.480 --> 32:24.240
I need to hurry

32:24.319 --> 32:25.440
and make an appointment with my tailor, Master Fang

32:25.480 --> 32:26.039
Set up a meeting

32:26.319 --> 32:27.519
My clothes are all embroidered

32:27.559 --> 32:28.240
They’re really nice

32:28.319 --> 32:29.279
I’ll introduce you next time

32:29.640 --> 32:30.680
I’m leaving, Xu, thank you

32:33.279 --> 32:33.799
Yanyan

32:42.839 --> 32:43.559
Auntie Yu

32:44.240 --> 32:45.839
It’s not easy to run a show

32:46.680 --> 32:49.480
How can you just pass favors

32:49.519 --> 32:50.680
onto me so casually?

32:51.640 --> 32:52.559
The caliber of the guests

32:52.920 --> 32:54.079
determines the quality of the show

32:54.079 --> 32:54.720
and its value

32:55.359 --> 32:56.400
I’m just a planner

32:56.640 --> 32:57.680
and the host in front of the camera

32:58.119 --> 32:59.599
My influence is limited

33:00.480 --> 33:01.559
But you’re different

33:02.000 --> 33:04.000
I believe with you by my side

33:04.200 --> 33:06.319
guiding me and paving the way

33:07.279 --> 33:09.400
I can build a good reputation

33:09.519 --> 33:10.880
and produce higher-quality shows

33:15.359 --> 33:16.039
Come, sit

33:21.799 --> 33:23.039
There are many capable people

33:24.319 --> 33:25.519
but few with real vision

33:27.720 --> 33:29.400
I still need to learn from you

33:30.599 --> 33:31.400
You’re promising

33:45.640 --> 33:46.440
Auntie Yu

33:46.559 --> 33:47.319
Careful, it’s hot

33:54.400 --> 33:56.759
If you want to seize every chance to turn things around

33:57.680 --> 33:59.000
never pin your hopes

33:59.000 --> 34:00.559
on someone else

34:01.839 --> 34:03.119
It’s just

34:04.720 --> 34:05.720
using what you have

34:07.799 --> 34:08.840
to get what you want

34:12.000 --> 34:12.920
Xu

34:14.280 --> 34:16.079
This episode turned out really well

34:16.480 --> 34:17.760
Great reputation and high ratings

34:18.039 --> 34:18.679
Impressive

34:19.119 --> 34:20.199
Keep doing it this way

34:22.840 --> 34:23.480
Director

34:24.840 --> 34:27.119
After Sun Siwei

34:27.800 --> 34:28.920
Don’t worry about her

34:29.320 --> 34:30.280
I’ve sent her to do field reports

34:30.599 --> 34:31.719
You know her temper

34:31.960 --> 34:32.639
She can make a fuss

34:33.480 --> 34:35.159
but she can’t argue with the show’s quality

34:35.840 --> 34:37.159
So she has nothing to complain about

34:38.840 --> 34:39.920
Thank you for your support, Director

34:40.079 --> 34:40.760
Your ideas are good

34:40.800 --> 34:41.960
Of course I’ll support you

34:43.719 --> 34:44.360
Xu

34:46.480 --> 34:47.480
You just said

34:48.199 --> 34:49.840
there was something else you wanted to tell me?

34:51.000 --> 34:52.880
It’s about the program’s naming rights fee

34:56.360 --> 34:57.280
This company

34:57.360 --> 34:58.960
keeps pushing me to sign the contract

34:59.199 --> 35:00.599
The naming rights fee is

35:00.679 --> 35:02.199
12% higher than before

35:02.920 --> 35:04.199
If you think it’s okay

35:04.760 --> 35:05.760
we can proceed

35:08.079 --> 35:09.199
Why are you coming to me

35:09.199 --> 35:10.360
about the naming rights fee?

35:10.719 --> 35:11.239
President Liu

35:12.239 --> 35:13.239
Now it’s me

35:13.800 --> 35:14.920
This is the latest

35:14.920 --> 35:16.159
Family Banquet guest list

35:16.239 --> 35:16.920
Please take a look

35:19.760 --> 35:20.880
Are you sure these people

35:20.920 --> 35:21.679
can all be invited?

35:21.760 --> 35:22.840
You can put it in the contract

35:23.480 --> 35:25.079
But the latest naming rights fee

35:25.599 --> 35:26.960
is 12% higher

35:32.280 --> 35:33.239
Xu

35:34.239 --> 35:35.280
I knew you wouldn’t

35:35.280 --> 35:36.719
let me down

35:38.760 --> 35:39.320
Sign it

35:50.480 --> 35:51.000
Xu Yan

35:51.239 --> 35:51.880
Did you see it?

35:51.920 --> 35:52.760
Director Zhou just saw

35:52.760 --> 35:53.960
the latest weekly report and his reaction

35:54.079 --> 35:55.400
He was all smiles

35:55.960 --> 35:57.639
Our show made a comeback against the odds

35:58.159 --> 35:59.719
The celebrities' phones are ringing off the hook

35:59.760 --> 36:01.159
Everyone's super enthusiastic

36:02.199 --> 36:04.199
We've secured the top trending star for the next episode

36:04.199 --> 36:04.920
That's settled too

36:06.400 --> 36:07.039
Thank you

36:10.599 --> 36:11.119
Sis

36:11.199 --> 36:12.159
What are you doing?

36:12.320 --> 36:13.199
I can't accept this money

36:13.760 --> 36:15.440
Isn't your dad in the hospital?

36:15.920 --> 36:16.840
You need money for the surgery

36:16.840 --> 36:17.760
Don't be so polite with me

36:19.440 --> 36:20.800
You introduced Director Lu to me

36:21.039 --> 36:22.159
I'm already very grateful

36:22.599 --> 36:23.519
If it weren't for you

36:23.639 --> 36:24.400
I wouldn't have met

36:24.440 --> 36:25.440
such an important director

36:27.000 --> 36:27.599
Huanhuan

36:28.639 --> 36:30.159
Resources are meant to be used

36:30.800 --> 36:31.679
And you should know

36:32.159 --> 36:33.760
The surgery is the most important thing right now

36:36.360 --> 36:37.599
I hope the surgery goes smoothly

36:39.599 --> 36:41.119
You've been running back and forth lately

36:41.159 --> 36:42.239
It's really tough

36:42.480 --> 36:43.679
Eat a bit more today, get some energy back

36:43.800 --> 36:44.440
What do you want to eat?

36:45.519 --> 36:46.280
It's my treat

36:49.360 --> 36:50.039
What would you like?

36:51.320 --> 36:52.119
The usual three dishes

36:52.320 --> 36:52.760
Okay

36:57.639 --> 36:58.880
Congratulations, Xu Yan

36:58.920 --> 37:00.280
You became the host of Family Banquet

37:00.519 --> 37:01.559
You've worked so hard for this show

37:01.559 --> 37:02.559
You've put in so much effort

37:02.639 --> 37:04.039
We all see it

37:06.639 --> 37:07.559
Thank you, Sister Liao

37:08.320 --> 37:08.719
By the way

37:08.840 --> 37:10.400
Join us for dinner tonight

37:11.119 --> 37:12.360
You're too polite

37:16.199 --> 37:16.960
Sister Siwei

37:17.199 --> 37:18.679
Why did you come so early?

37:18.840 --> 37:19.960
What do you mean by that?

37:20.559 --> 37:21.519
Sister Siwei always

37:21.559 --> 37:22.480
gets her makeup done at this time

37:22.679 --> 37:23.039
No

37:23.119 --> 37:24.119
Your outdoor shoot

37:24.159 --> 37:25.239
is at six in the evening

37:25.400 --> 37:26.719
It's scheduled after Family Banquet

37:27.079 --> 37:28.880
And it's only three o'clock now

37:29.159 --> 37:29.840
Don't people usually

37:29.840 --> 37:31.239
come two hours early for makeup?

37:31.360 --> 37:32.519
The show is the show

37:32.599 --> 37:33.760
Makeup is makeup

37:34.280 --> 37:35.599
Since when does the makeup team

37:35.599 --> 37:36.559
have so much power

37:36.559 --> 37:37.239
that they can decide

37:37.239 --> 37:38.519
when we record the show?

37:40.280 --> 37:40.760
I

37:42.000 --> 37:43.039
So I can't get my makeup done, is that it?

37:43.360 --> 37:43.920
Fine, come on

37:44.039 --> 37:44.679
Give me your phone

37:45.480 --> 37:45.920
No

37:46.079 --> 37:47.719
I'll call Director Zhou and ask

37:47.760 --> 37:48.800
If today's outdoor shoot

37:48.800 --> 37:49.840
runs overtime

37:49.880 --> 37:52.000
who's responsible if we miss the daylight?

37:52.079 --> 37:52.920
No, Sister Siwei

37:52.960 --> 37:53.840
That's not what I meant

37:53.840 --> 37:54.360
I mean

37:54.400 --> 37:54.960
Sister Liao

37:56.559 --> 37:57.559
You can do her makeup first

37:57.679 --> 37:58.400
I can wait

37:59.840 --> 38:00.440
Okay

38:00.800 --> 38:01.400
Sister Siwei

38:01.679 --> 38:03.159
Please wait a moment

38:03.360 --> 38:05.079
I'll get your touch-up kit

38:16.320 --> 38:17.800
You need a touch-up now

38:18.280 --> 38:19.320
We're heading out for the shoot soon

38:19.400 --> 38:20.239
Your makeup will be ruined

38:20.639 --> 38:21.960
Why make things difficult for others?

38:24.039 --> 38:25.800
She really thinks she's something special

38:26.760 --> 38:28.840
She's only recorded one episode

38:29.679 --> 38:30.400
Don't really think

38:30.440 --> 38:31.719
you're on the same level as me

38:32.360 --> 38:33.960
Other shows have invited me too

38:34.599 --> 38:35.800
But I'm worried about you

38:36.880 --> 38:37.679
When I host

38:37.679 --> 38:39.119
the average rating is four

38:39.559 --> 38:40.840
When you host, it's one

38:42.119 --> 38:43.000
How am I supposed to leave?

38:47.480 --> 38:48.199
That proposal of yours

38:48.199 --> 38:49.400
Did you do it yourself?

38:49.679 --> 38:51.199
Your boyfriend probably bought it for you

38:51.880 --> 38:53.559
You know my abilities well

38:53.920 --> 38:54.800
These proposals

38:54.840 --> 38:55.760
are done by me and my team

38:55.800 --> 38:56.719
We can handle them ourselves

38:57.159 --> 38:58.480
I don't need my boyfriend's help

38:59.679 --> 39:00.800
If you can't beat me

39:01.280 --> 39:03.199
you find a rich boyfriend to back you up

39:03.559 --> 39:04.119
Xu Yan

39:04.119 --> 39:05.199
How come I never knew

39:05.199 --> 39:06.280
you were so ambitious

39:06.280 --> 39:07.119
and so resourceful

39:11.559 --> 39:12.639
I can get exclusives

39:14.159 --> 39:15.280
handle the whole process

39:16.639 --> 39:18.000
and have professional skills

39:19.119 --> 39:20.360
Why shouldn't I compete?

39:23.440 --> 39:24.239
I've never thought

39:24.239 --> 39:25.239
being ambitious and resourceful

39:25.239 --> 39:26.199
was a bad thing

39:27.280 --> 39:28.360
I'll take that as a compliment

39:28.760 --> 39:29.480
Thank you

39:39.880 --> 39:41.519
Is she really that shameless?

39:41.639 --> 39:42.360
Yeah

39:46.679 --> 39:48.320
When she first joined

39:48.519 --> 39:50.039
I clearly remember

39:50.039 --> 39:52.440
she said she only had a grandma at home

39:53.400 --> 39:55.519
When did her parents end up abroad?

39:55.760 --> 39:56.920
Now she's from an intellectual family?

39:57.199 --> 39:58.000
Do you think she

39:58.039 --> 39:59.159
is hiding her background like on reality shows

39:59.599 --> 40:00.679
pretending to be someone else

40:00.840 --> 40:02.400
working part-time to experience life?

40:02.559 --> 40:03.239
No way

40:04.079 --> 40:04.960
With how poor she looks

40:04.960 --> 40:05.920
She doesn't seem like she's faking it

40:06.679 --> 40:07.639
That's for sure

40:08.239 --> 40:09.039
A few days ago

40:09.039 --> 40:09.880
I saw her wearing

40:09.880 --> 40:10.760
a diamond bracelet

40:11.119 --> 40:12.440
Each stone was a carat

40:13.320 --> 40:14.239
And she's marrying

40:14.239 --> 40:15.679
the heir to a construction empire, right?

40:16.239 --> 40:17.239
Families like that

40:17.599 --> 40:18.920
care most about matching backgrounds

40:27.599 --> 40:28.239
Xu Yan

40:29.880 --> 40:31.119
I've sent the proposal to your email

40:31.199 --> 40:32.239
Is there anything else?

40:32.960 --> 40:34.079
Remember to send the interview questions

40:34.079 --> 40:35.159
to the guests in advance

40:35.880 --> 40:36.239
Okay

40:36.480 --> 40:37.239
I'll head off now

40:37.360 --> 40:37.840
Go ahead

40:53.719 --> 40:54.880
Good evening, everyone.

40:55.159 --> 40:55.800
Welcome to

40:55.800 --> 40:56.920
tonight's financial news.

40:57.480 --> 40:59.119
This year, global stock markets have faced

40:59.239 --> 41:00.719
new opportunities and challenges.

41:00.719 --> 41:01.360
On one hand,

41:01.480 --> 41:03.199
the aftermath of the tech stock bubble burst

41:03.280 --> 41:04.760
continues to affect market confidence.

41:05.000 --> 41:05.760
On the other hand,

41:05.920 --> 41:07.119
the rise of emerging markets

41:07.280 --> 41:08.000
offers investors

41:08.000 --> 41:09.440
new growth opportunities.

41:09.480 --> 41:10.480
China, with its

41:10.480 --> 41:11.880
stable economic policies

41:12.079 --> 41:13.599
and vast market potential,

41:13.760 --> 41:15.119
has attracted global attention.

41:15.400 --> 41:16.679
Qiao Yan is recovering well.

41:16.920 --> 41:18.440
She'll be discharged in two days.

41:19.159 --> 41:20.239
Thank you, doctor.

41:20.400 --> 41:20.920
Thank you.

41:21.079 --> 41:21.800
After leaving the hospital,

41:21.920 --> 41:22.599
make sure the child

41:22.639 --> 41:23.639
gets enough sleep

41:23.840 --> 41:24.599
and doesn't get too tired.

41:24.760 --> 41:25.440
I will.

41:25.440 --> 41:27.079
I'll take good care of her.

41:27.199 --> 41:27.760
Good.

41:28.159 --> 41:30.199
Acquiring and sharing cultural information

41:31.920 --> 41:33.280
has also made China's stock market

41:33.360 --> 41:34.480
a hotspot for international capital

41:34.639 --> 41:35.760
to compete for.

41:35.800 --> 41:36.320
Yan Yan,

41:40.760 --> 41:41.679
how did you get up here?

41:42.239 --> 41:44.199
I ran into Huan Huan downstairs.

41:44.320 --> 41:45.159
She swiped her card for me.

41:47.719 --> 41:48.960
You're the only one left?

41:49.400 --> 41:50.159
Still working overtime?

41:52.599 --> 41:53.800
Is there anything I can help with?

41:55.440 --> 41:56.119
What a coincidence.

41:56.559 --> 41:57.719
I happen to have a few dishes

41:57.719 --> 41:58.559
I'm undecided about.

41:58.800 --> 41:59.599
You have the best taste.

41:59.719 --> 42:00.599
Help me choose.

42:01.480 --> 42:02.119
Take a look.

42:02.360 --> 42:02.800
Let's go.

42:05.199 --> 42:06.000
So, look here.

42:06.239 --> 42:07.679
This is the Hangzhou cuisine series.

42:07.840 --> 42:09.960
This is Longjing Shrimp.

42:10.199 --> 42:10.920
The recipe is here.

42:11.079 --> 42:12.119
This is Dongpo Pork.

42:13.679 --> 42:14.360
And this is

42:15.239 --> 42:16.320
a pearl necklace.

42:20.719 --> 42:21.400
Congratulations

42:21.559 --> 42:22.360
on winning the job competition.

42:23.320 --> 42:24.280
This is a gift for Family Banquet's

42:24.280 --> 42:25.360
female host.

42:28.559 --> 42:29.159
Thank you.

42:29.639 --> 42:31.280
Your surprises always arrive first.

42:32.840 --> 42:33.480
Do you like it?

42:33.639 --> 42:34.599
Of course I do.

42:38.599 --> 42:40.239
Now that I'm officially the female host,

42:40.760 --> 42:42.199
do I get my own office?

42:42.519 --> 42:43.880
Program hosts don't get one.

42:44.719 --> 42:46.480
But news anchors

42:46.719 --> 42:47.880
do have their own office.

42:49.840 --> 42:51.360
Then I'll become a news anchor.

42:57.440 --> 42:58.400
News anchor

42:58.760 --> 43:00.159
The competition is intense.

43:00.719 --> 43:01.760
Especially for someone like me,

43:01.840 --> 43:03.400
who has never hosted the news before.

43:03.960 --> 43:05.000
It's even harder.

43:06.079 --> 43:07.559
It might be tough for others,

43:08.400 --> 43:09.239
but for you,

43:10.239 --> 43:12.000
I've always had faith in you.

43:14.079 --> 43:14.679
I always feel

43:14.679 --> 43:15.679
you can turn the impossible

43:15.760 --> 43:16.480
into possible.

43:18.840 --> 43:20.239
You believe I can do it.

43:21.119 --> 43:22.480
Go for whatever you want.

43:23.360 --> 43:24.039
I'm still waiting

43:24.039 --> 43:25.239
to throw you a celebration party.

43:28.079 --> 43:29.280
But first,

43:29.679 --> 43:31.079
let's solve your problems.

43:31.360 --> 43:32.239
Finish work quickly.

43:32.639 --> 43:33.679
It's getting late.

43:37.920 --> 43:38.719
Everything is moving

43:38.719 --> 43:40.519
in the direction I hoped for.

43:41.400 --> 43:42.840
But I never thought

43:43.360 --> 43:44.880
a lie could be flawless.

43:45.599 --> 43:46.880
It only tightens around my throat,

43:46.880 --> 43:48.079
making it harder to breathe.

43:48.519 --> 43:50.159
I can barely catch my breath.

43:51.360 --> 43:52.519
Maybe the reason for lying

43:52.519 --> 43:53.960
isn't to deceive others,

43:54.800 --> 43:56.119
but to deceive myself.

43:57.800 --> 43:59.440
The family I tried to erase

44:00.519 --> 44:02.519
was never truly gone.

44:05.679 --> 44:06.400
Look at this one.

44:07.039 --> 44:08.039
It's really great.

44:09.840 --> 44:10.679
Before, our group of sisters

44:10.679 --> 44:11.760
had similar activities.

44:12.000 --> 44:13.119
They were all pretty much the same.

44:13.800 --> 44:15.440
Everyone got bored a long time ago.

44:16.000 --> 44:17.280
Your program is really special.

44:17.599 --> 44:18.800
Now everyone is so enthusiastic.

44:18.920 --> 44:20.480
You even need connections to join.

44:21.679 --> 44:22.239
That's true.

44:22.599 --> 44:23.480
Smart people,

44:23.559 --> 44:25.840
know how to use their resources.

44:25.880 --> 44:26.519
Right?

44:27.800 --> 44:29.280
Honestly, I didn't understand this before.

44:29.320 --> 44:29.920
Uncle

44:30.400 --> 44:30.840
Thank you.

44:30.840 --> 44:31.920
It's only after spending time with Auntie

44:31.960 --> 44:32.800
for a while recently,

44:33.039 --> 44:34.440
and attending several banquets,

44:34.760 --> 44:35.639
that I've learned a little.

44:35.639 --> 44:36.400
Just the basics.

44:37.400 --> 44:38.480
You're such a sweet talker.

44:40.000 --> 44:40.760
You little rascal.

44:40.760 --> 44:42.039
Can you slow down?

44:42.280 --> 44:43.239
I want to watch cartoons.

44:43.639 --> 44:44.239
Did you finish your homework?

44:44.239 --> 44:44.840
Slow down, don't trip.

44:44.960 --> 44:45.960
Is your homework done? Yes.

44:46.079 --> 44:46.679
We agreed

44:46.760 --> 44:47.719
you can only watch for half an hour.

44:47.960 --> 44:49.000
You're spoiling him again.

44:50.159 --> 44:50.880
Have some tea.

44:51.119 --> 44:51.840
Next,

44:51.880 --> 44:52.880
let's welcome with applause

44:53.320 --> 44:53.800
Dad

44:53.920 --> 44:54.920
Isn't this you?

44:55.280 --> 44:56.400
Mr. Shen Jinsong

44:56.519 --> 44:58.039
and representatives of the businesses

44:58.280 --> 44:59.760
for the commercial street renovation project

44:59.840 --> 45:01.039
to cut the ribbon.

45:01.280 --> 45:03.159
Let's count down together.

45:04.679 --> 45:05.199
Three

45:05.599 --> 45:06.159
Two

45:06.400 --> 45:06.880
One

45:07.159 --> 45:08.599
Please cut the ribbon.

45:09.400 --> 45:10.960
Let's give a round of applause.

45:11.039 --> 45:12.360
Yunjiangli, Dayun County

45:12.559 --> 45:14.199
Honey, you look good on camera.

45:15.320 --> 45:16.639
You're not too old to be seen yet.

45:16.800 --> 45:17.360
Right?

45:17.480 --> 45:18.760
Let's move to the center together

45:18.880 --> 45:19.800
for a group photo.

45:21.840 --> 45:23.119
How do you feel?

45:25.320 --> 45:26.239
Well, very...

45:26.320 --> 45:27.000
I, I, I...

45:27.400 --> 45:28.800
On behalf of the commercial street,

45:29.079 --> 45:29.920
all the businesses,

45:31.320 --> 45:32.440
I thank Jinda Group

45:33.079 --> 45:34.559
and Chairman Shen

45:34.920 --> 45:35.719
for providing us

45:36.000 --> 45:37.320
with a great

45:37.960 --> 45:38.800
business environment

45:39.360 --> 45:40.440
and promoting business growth.

45:41.559 --> 45:42.920
We will continue as always

45:43.320 --> 45:44.239
to fulfill our duties

45:44.800 --> 45:46.679
and serve our community well.

45:46.920 --> 45:47.920
It's reported that Yunjiangli

45:48.079 --> 45:48.679
Xu, by the way,

45:49.000 --> 45:50.239
you're from Shanxi, right?

45:50.239 --> 45:51.400
is a key project for urban development

45:51.440 --> 45:53.000
and improving residents' quality of life.

45:53.000 --> 45:54.039
It's a representative project.

45:54.400 --> 45:55.679
The old Yunjiangli district

45:55.840 --> 45:56.559
had narrow roads.

45:56.559 --> 45:57.000
Yes.

45:57.320 --> 45:57.960
Well...

45:58.079 --> 45:59.320
Have you ever been to Dayun County?

45:59.480 --> 46:00.559
The streets have been widened,

46:00.840 --> 46:02.280
and accessible pathways have been added.

46:02.440 --> 46:03.639
And throughout the business district,

46:03.880 --> 46:04.920
My grandma is

46:05.000 --> 46:06.639
from Yunlai Village, Dayun County.
